WEBVTT

00:00.300 --> 00:05.300
Lagging Theory is not a delay model.

00:05.300 --> 00:12.000
It tests when gradient and flux fall out of sync.

00:12.000 --> 00:20.000
Delayed response can come from storage, leakage, exchange, or coupling.

00:20.000 --> 00:28.000
A fitted curve can still transfer the wrong parameter.

00:28.000 --> 00:36.750
The test is whether pumping limits, recovery time, or a design threshold changes.

00:36.750 --> 00:42.500
Use lag only when it changes the decision.
